Report the health of **{{PROJECT_NAME}}**.

Run `doctrina status` for the dashboard (index drift, framework stamp,
coverage %, trace anchors, verify config, artifact counts). For the
authoritative gates run `doctrina validate` and `doctrina verify`, and
`doctrina next` for the recommended action.

Summarise what is green, what is not, and the single next step.
